OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be a few showers
OL,6,Fthrough the morning, otherwise dry
OL,7,Fwith some bright or sunny intervals.
OL,8,FCold but the occasionally fresh
OL,9,Fnortherly wind easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some brightness at
OL,12,Ffirst, but cloud and rain spread west
OL,13,Finto Orkney through the evening,
OL,14,Freaching Shetland overnight. Clearer
OL,15,Fspells and blustery showers arriving
OL,16,Fby morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
