OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloud and rain soon clearing
OL,6,FShetland. Otherwise bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells and scattered showers. Drier
OL,8,Ffor a time in the afternoon. Blustery
OL,9,Fwest to northwest winds, easing in the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,13,Fcold with sunny spells and scattered
OL,14,Fheavy showers through Wednesday and
OL,15,FThursday. Breezy at times on Thursday.
OL,16,FMostly dry and bright Friday, but the
OL,17,Fodd shower possible first thing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
